\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Here is the definition of a word that will allow data entry for a single
 record (person):
\end_layout

\begin_layout Scrap
<<enter-person>>=
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

: enter-person   PEOPLE  SLOT READ
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

    CR ." Name? "     NAME ASK
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

    CR ." Address? "  STREET ASK
\begin_inset Newline newline
