By invoking 
\family typewriter
\series bold
PEOPLE
\family default
\series default
, we select the 
\family typewriter
\series bold
PEOPLE
\family default
\series default
 file as the current file.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The word 
\family typewriter
\series bold
SLOT
\family default
\series default
 allocates a new record in the current file, and leaves its number on the
 stack (see 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "sub:Record-Allocation/Deallocation-Operators"

\end_inset

).
 The word 
\family typewriter
\series bold
READ
\family default
\series default
